{"tid":1376460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[光復香港] 警訊教你見唔到委任證唔好show ID ！！！","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T01:11:58.000Z","uid":221192,"like":146,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b6963ae527cd1fb2110ebc183fa8edffcffd68e2","tid":1376460,"uid":221192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:32:02.000Z","msg":"見到好多手足出入發夢都俾死黑狗攔截check ID，琴日元朗個姐姐就做得好好啦，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">見唔到委任證</span></span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好俾身份證</span></span></strong>d死黑狗！！！<br />\n<br />\n警訊教我地，要做個良好市民，唔好輕易相信賊人，因為香港真係好好好好好危險架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前果排就發生左好多假冒警務人員事件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88rNNtr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88rNNtr.png&h=62d0c6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢兩位警務人員就教我地點樣做返個奉公守法既良好市民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ZPcd8N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ZPcd8N.png&h=a990f479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dN5622C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdN5622C.png&h=7dbf9efb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢仲再三叮囑我地千其唔好上當，成為不法之徒既獵物呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdufWn9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdufWn9.png&h=5d659a85&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tH9Pgob.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtH9Pgob.png&h=ef7fe555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料來源：RTHK 6月19日播放的警訊<br />\n<br />\n作為愛護香港、奉公守法既良好市民，我地一定要時刻警覺，提防一切罪案發生<br />\n所以當大家見到有可疑人士（惡形惡相果d呢）話要攞身份證黎睇，記得<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">問佢攞左委任證黎睇先</span></span></strong>。正所謂佛度眾生，係路上面有人有可能犯左<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">假冒公職人員</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">管有虛假文書</span></span></strong>呢d罪，我地一定要盡能力勸佢地回頭是岸呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n最後不厭其煩都係要再提，就算隻死黑狗真係攞到狗狗證出黎，我地淨係需要俾自己身份證佢睇，其他問題一律唔需要回答架！佢地無權搜身，除非佢有合理懷疑你進行緊犯罪活動。所以大家千其千其唔好俾d惡形惡相既死黑狗嚇親或者兇到，佢地係狗係毅進仔黎咋！！！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做！"},{"pid":"486598f6298f8f475d71f1fe99e895faad27fb4c","tid":1376460,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:32:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[728] 需要地方落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1f4f7214e23b2168a7199ccb00cf35a87de31f","tid":1376460,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:33:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88ef0fbc0fa9a5a292eb97b8f72f696c104a295d","tid":1376460,"uid":221192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:35:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ed44418c3b8a7606a447ec09a1f863f4d62e4b8e","tid":1376460,"uid":76463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"2604699efeab0625653ee5bef4a5f9691e1ff45d","tid":1376460,"uid":259945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:36:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9dc207d41aceb987bb4cfd5ad4566d815f0e0d7","tid":1376460,"uid":221192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:36:58.0